```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
npm test

# Watch mode
npm test -- --watch

# Coverage
npm test -- --coverage

# Specific file
npm test -- src/lib/utils/colors.test.ts
```

## Skip Tests for MVP

Focus on utilities and hooks first. Skip these for initial build:
- E2E tests
- Visual tests
- Animation tests
- Integration tests with real Spotify API
